Introduction

nginx-xdata is a keyword filter module for nginx.


Install

$ git clone git://github.com/roast/nginx-xdata.git
$ wget 'http://sysoev.ru/nginx/nginx-0.7.65.tar.gz'
$ tar -xzvf nginx-0.7.65.tar.gz
$ cd nginx-0.0.7.65/
$ ./configure --add-module=/absolute/path/to/the/nginx-xdata/
$ make
$ make install


Directives 

*xdata*
syntax: xdata[ on|off ]
default: xdata off
context: http, server, location
Enables or disables the keyword filter module. 

*xdata_word_file*
syntax: xdata_word_file path 
context: http, server, location
The xdata_word_file directive sets the path of the keyword file. 


